{"tid":1872801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"駐極體(包括N95)口罩經五種不同消毒方式後，過濾 14.6~594 nm 煙霧質(Aersol)之效能","createTime":"2020-02-10T09:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T16:09:22.000Z","uid":170229,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"15430d0f8f8b5d4b2b9d0903569d0deddb20c3b6","tid":1872801,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:15:07.000Z","msg":"Lin, T. H., Chen, C. C., Huang, S. H., Kuo, C. W., Lai, C. Y., &amp; Lin, W. Y. (2017). Filter quality of electret masks in filtering 14.6&ndash;594 nm aerosol particles: Effects of five decontamination methods. <em>Plos One, 12</em>(10). doi: 10.1371/journal.pone.0186217<br />\n<br />\n實驗方式: 口罩切開六份，一份作Control，其他會被消毒<br />\n消毒方式: <br />\n1. 電飯煲 149~164&deg;C 不加水，3分鐘<br />\n2. 滅菌釜 121&deg;C , 1.06 kg cm&minus;2 ，15分鐘<br />\n3. 70% 乙醇，10分鐘, 然後風乾一晚<br />\n4.  100% 異丙醇, 10分鐘 , 然後風乾一晚<br />\n5. 0.5% 次氯酸鈉, 10分鐘 , 然後風乾一晚<br />\nSet-up:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9eCBgrL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9eCBgrL.jpg&h=196780b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NwMiuNr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNwMiuNr.jpg&h=750b7272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3FUsn7s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3FUsn7s.jpg&h=fbd88d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5s9DuNs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5s9DuNs.jpg&h=b60be889&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i0tQkT8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi0tQkT8.jpg&h=bea136c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WjOpqkO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWjOpqkO.jpg&h=a8013211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2CnJFT9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt