},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:38:38.000Z","msg":"或者睇下面5幅圖，右上係消毒方法，x軸係粒子大細，而y軸係通過率<br />\n每pair curves (紅黑/青黃/藍粉紅) 越接近代表過濾能力越冇受影響，當中電飯煲每pair curve接近一樣，所以電飯煲最好<br />\n(幅圖亦可以睇到唔同標準用黎測試嘅0.3 &mu;m，即係300 nm，亦即係右邊條虛線，係最難過濾)"},{"pid":"fd0296a89ef416696e29c387217980181aec475a","tid":1872801,"uid":201605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:52:15.000Z","msg":"無Conclusion?"},{"pid":"a3f79b078abc9999dac50b2fbd3feb0fb1beb1ab","tid":1872801,"uid":10788,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T10:07:49.000Z","msg":"要驗埋消毒前後個病毒數量<br />\n如果唔係個方法幾有效都好 可能蒸完都殺唔到病毒"},{"pid":"cc2634e0d52136748fb1245f8eb10aa5b339d22b","tid":1872801,"uid":280329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T10:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />炒電飯煲"},{"pid":"089fe824d77979343dac5518226c88697f1cc9b3","tid":1872801,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd0296a89ef416696e29c387217980181aec475a","tid":1872801,"uid":201605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:52:15.000Z","msg":"無Conclusion?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:10:19.000Z","msg":"用電飯煲，無水加熱，對n95過濾能力最無影響"},{"pid":"6a4c2dbde8d70dafa266d641193afab5f5e5741d","tid":1872801,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98e4a6bfa6ffae933e4d3af6e3c2df0d46f8a216","tid":1872801,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:23:11.000Z","msg":"即係點邊個方法最好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:10:32.000Z","msg":"用電飯煲，無水加熱，對n95過濾能力最無影響"},{"pid":"212b5e0e23836b58ac40201918e74a0ba477cd7e","tid":1872801,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7630880848ce11a549b36cc6fc379a4f57ff0646","tid":1872801,"uid":63298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sorry 我蠢，唔識睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10