https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5s9DuNs.jpg&h=b60be889&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i0tQkT8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi0tQkT8.jpg&h=bea136c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WjOpqkO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWjOpqkO.jpg&h=a8013211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2CnJFT9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2CnJFT9.jpg&h=cc5d1812&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:16:37.000Z","msg":"講下個結果，唔係人人識睇圖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:11:06.000Z","msg":"用電飯煲，無水加熱，對n95過濾能力最無影響"},{"pid":"44b9ffdafe4df972367aad8126f053fbed6bed13","tid":1872801,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:14:45.000Z","msg":"用微波爐得唔得?"},{"pid":"359f505e6c6562bea326f661422295a214e09cbc","tid":1872801,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3f79b078abc9999dac50b2fbd3feb0fb1beb1ab","tid":1872801,"uid":10788,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T10:07:49.000Z","msg":"要驗埋消毒前後個病毒數量<br />\n如果唔係個方法幾有效都好 可能蒸完都殺唔到病毒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:20:31.000Z","msg":"呢個難搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過就sars 黎講：<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Heating the virus at 56 degrees C for 5 min dramatically reduced the infectivity of the virus from 2.6 x 10(7) to 40 TCID50/ml, whereas heating the virus for 60 min or longer eliminated all infectivity. &quot;<br />\n<br />\n我地用三倍溫度，但只係三分鐘，唔知效果如何。"},{"pid":"498b832d1bc0c174da3698633619cbf283097729","tid":1872801,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:31:51.000Z","msg":"a,b 3D graphs代表300&micro;m/75&micro;m particles? 點解大粒D穿透會易D"},{"pid":"124f7c48e8767e43426c0fb2d64ab7eaedc8932e","tid":1872801,"uid":170229,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"498b832d1bc0c174da3698633619cbf283097729","tid":1872801,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:31:51.000Z","msg":"a,b 3D graphs代表300&micro;m/75&micro;m particles? 點解大粒D穿透會易D"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:35:56.000Z","msg":"據我理解，大粒同細粒嘅過濾原理唔同。 大粒係直接穿唔到過去口罩另一面，細粒係用靜電捉住。所以擋到大粒唔一定捉到細粒，反之亦然。"},{"pid":"c40599d44cf517327888d47981b51aad230d1f22","tid":1872801,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"124f7c48e8767e43426c0fb2d64ab7eaedc8932e","tid":1872801,"uid":170229,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"498b832d1bc0c174da3698633619cbf283097729","tid":1872801,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:31:51.000Z","msg":"a,b 3D graphs代表300&micro;m/75&micro;m particles? 點解大粒D穿透會易D"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:35:56.000Z","msg":"據我理解，大粒同細粒嘅過濾原理唔同。 大粒係直接穿唔到過去口罩另一面，細粒係用靜電捉住。所以擋到大粒唔一定捉到細粒，反之亦然。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:36:47.000Z","msg":"如果有專家想補充嘅話我無任歡迎。"},{"pid":"5365af5792a6bf838ae9086d151bf28be301f460","tid":1872801,"uid":170229,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"498b832d1bc0c174da3698633619cbf283097729","tid":1872801,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:31:51.000Z","msg":"a,b 3D graphs代表300&micro;m/75&micro;m particles? 點解大粒D穿透會易D"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:43:31.000Z","msg":"借用之前其他連登仔嘅source<br />\n<br />\n台灣cdc:<br />\n<br />\n細小粒徑的微粒本身會有隨 意震動的特性(擴散作用，就像有機蒸氣在靜止的教室前面，慢慢擴散到教 室後面)，再者微粒粒徑越小相同質量下會有更大的表面積，容易產生靜電， 且在帶相同靜電電荷下，靜電力作用會更明顯，這二個擴散及靜電作用，對 於越細小粒徑之微粒都越強烈，因此捕集效率都會增加。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov.tw/File/Get/UoQPKjRwFFPoijcoUyn-9Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov.tw%2FFile%2FGet%2FUoQPKjRwFFPoijcoUyn-9Q&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=d120d20c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cdc.gov.tw/File/Get/UoQPKjRwFFPoijcoUyn-9Q</a>"},{"pid":"62cb8044877d99023b60be3e0a71334e70ce9d7c","tid":1872801,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:44:34.000Z","msg":"電飯煲 之前同之後好似冇分別咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59da5c44a86e4219519ba599ca6297a7e047d5f2","tid":1872801,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:45:25.000Z","msg":"樓主冇改錯名"},{"pid":"237f6b5852176019ac6db38635cb5a46e57dcdb1","tid":1872801,"uid":102701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:00:52.000Z","msg":"咁電飯煲加熱中途，未到太高溫，口罩d菌唔會飛出嚟成個廚房都係咩？"},{"pid":"d2f677157d805a12ff41a25e9b67bca2b6d24e6e","tid":1872801,"uid":298833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536b8b2e20a09da37eb57ce047c9cd1f7bce4171","tid":1872801,"uid":48330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:07:11.000Z","msg":"電飯煲可媲美Autoclave<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b3183171ed1102c92ae39f59b0fe561928d9184","tid":1872801,"uid":102588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"44b9ffdafe4df972367aad8126f053fbed6bed13","tid":1872801,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:14:45.000Z","msg":"用微波爐得唔得?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T14:06:28.000Z","msg":"應該唔得<br />\n微波爐靠加熱水分子"},{"pid":"8c829f0be8c3f4c1075ad07f28467d32bb8a6a74","tid":1872801,"uid":102588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"536b8b2e20a09da37eb57ce047c9cd1f7bce4171","tid":1872801,"uid":48330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:07:11.000Z","msg":"電飯煲可媲美Autoclave<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T14:07:31.000Z","msg":"好過autoclave<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ca99710b6a9fe65c029c2ef5d1387be5438bd4","tid":1872801,"uid":218288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T15:44:33.000Z","msg":"2017年,仲要參與嘅全部都係台灣學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果真係缺口罩嘅時侯感覺可以試下,電飯煲個方法應該係要預熱左先?"},{"pid":"e4a8c24747ef4f5d08ff97fa148a83f98d0496f0","tid":1872801,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"536b8b2e20a09da37eb57ce047c9cd1f7bce4171","tid":1872801,"uid":48330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:07:11.000Z","msg":"電飯煲可媲美Autoclave<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T23:56:27.000Z","msg":"好過autoclave<br />\n<br />\n篇文入面有講 autoclave 搞到個filter 變型<br />\n<br />\nDecontamination typically increased &Delta;p, but treatment in the autoclave did not do so for the N95 or Gauze masks. The low pressure drop results for these two types of masks were observed to be associated with folds of the inner and outer filter supports. These folds may reduce the uniformity of filter density, causing the air to flow through loose filter material in the mask, and reducing the resistance of the filter."},{"pid":"4e10d51291bdc3413ccd71579bdd90d785ce299a","tid":1872801,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"237f6b5852176019ac6db38635cb5a46e57dcdb1","tid":1872801,"uid":102701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:00:52.000Z","msg":"咁電飯煲加熱中途，未到太高溫，口罩d菌唔會飛出嚟成個廚房都係咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T23:57:21.000Z","msg":"點解會飛出黎<br />\n<br />\n電飯煲唔係合實，無風嘅咩？"},{"pid":"0d383f21df8edd1c6f6ad980fd863cd766c10629","tid":1872801,"uid":30032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4e10d51291bdc3413ccd71579bdd90d785ce299a","tid":1872801,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"237f6b5852176019ac6db38635cb5a46e57dcdb1","tid":1872801,"uid":102701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T13:00:52.000Z","msg":"咁電飯煲加熱中途，未到太高溫，口罩d菌唔會飛出嚟成個廚房都係咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T23:57:21.000Z","msg":"點解會飛出黎<br />\n<br />\n電飯煲唔係合實，無風嘅咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T00:18:22.000Z","msg":"如果電飯煲冇位出蒸氣咁煮飯未會爆炸囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19c0f77a4011e09783984ea89050b97e6cdc287","tid":1872801,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T00:21:56.000Z","msg":"無計殺菌力 無用"},{"pid":"7cc65fd5657e1f00337331a37ec851c82995a995","tid":1872801,"uid":246215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T00:41:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Experimental method: One mask cut into 6 pieces<br />\nOne piece untreated, other 5 pieces treated by the 5 decontamination method <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n使唔使咁慳。唔想講到咁白，個study係廢既，唔係睇完整mask既filtration能力。變型/移位所致既整體filtration效率下降冇計入。同埋得liquid decontamination 有overnight果度已經柒左，有wear and tear，charge dissipation over time."},{"pid":"ebc60914666d0f29c5753cce022c127ffae4e465","tid":1872801,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T00:45:20.000Z","msg":"電飯煲無水加熱五分鐘（乾燒）已壞電飯煲，日日一個電飯煲？"},{"pid":"77b9a329c29172505c378aa883486696c2bd5bf6","tid":1872801,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T00:58:26.000Z","msg":"密實袋+慢煮棒有無得諗？"},{"pid":"d9ff5314eae6e9c9ce24f90521e222a66bc3889c","tid":1872801,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebc60914666d0f29c5753cce022c127ffae4e465","tid":1872801,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T00:45:20.000Z","msg":"電飯煲無水加熱五分鐘（乾燒）已壞電飯煲，日日一個電飯煲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T01:00:25.000Z","msg":"焗爐"},{