,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T02:12:26.000Z","msg":"變型有講delta p, 定係delta p 唔夠？<br />\novernight 又點柒咗？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T05:05:04.000Z","msg":"一塊仔mask既delta P又點可以extrapolate到成個口罩，高溫/高壓有機會直頭令成個mask變型fit唔到 （就連delta P係咪真係咁有意義都有待商榷，佢只係一個好&quot;coarse&quot;既indicator）。得某D treatment overnight緊係柒啦，同effect of time confound晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有邊個會傻9到浸成10分鐘，頂盡1分鐘乜9都死晒啦，都仲未計拎返上黎佢有排都未evaporate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:10:56.000Z","msg":"Treatment of SARS-CoV with PVP-I products for 2 min reduced the virus infectivity from 1.17 x 10(6) TCID(50)/ml to below the detectable level. The efficacy of 70% ethanol was equivalent to that of PVP-I products. Fixation of SARS-CoV-infected Vero E6 cells with a fixative including formalin, glutaraldehyde, methanol and acetone for 5 min or longer eliminated all infectivity. Heating the virus at 56 degrees C for 60 min or longer reduced the infectivity of the virus from 2.6 x 10(7) to undetectable levels. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/m/pubmed/16490989/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fm%2Fpubmed%2F16490989%2F&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=f642363f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/m/pubmed/16490989/</a><br />\n<br />\n兩分鐘先below detectable level, 5分鐘先完全eliminate.<br />\n<br />\n變型呢樣嘢可以自己喺屋企試下<br />\n<br />\novernight 會唔會重係濕呢樣嘢我違下再細讀份paper"},{"pid":"7d9b95dbda26f924fde9f1111e6c2e2c032b916c","tid":1872801,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5365af5792a6bf838ae9086d151bf28be301f460","tid":1872801,"uid":170229,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"498b832d1bc0c174da3698633619cbf283097729","tid":1872801,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:31:51.000Z","msg":"a,b 3D graphs代表300&micro;m/75&micro;m particles? 點解大粒D穿透會易D"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:43:31.000Z","msg":"借用之前其他連登仔嘅source<br />\n<br />\n台灣cdc:<br />\n<br />\n細小粒徑的微粒本身會有隨 意震動的特性(擴散作用，就像有機蒸氣在靜止的教室前面，慢慢擴散到教 室後面)，再者微粒粒徑越小相同質量下會有更大的表面積，容易產生靜電， 且在帶相同靜電電荷下，靜電力作用會更明顯，這二個擴散及靜電作用，對 於越細小粒徑之微粒都越強烈，因此捕集效率都會增加。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov.tw/File/Get/UoQPKjRwFFPoijcoUyn-9Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov.tw%2FFile%2FGet%2FUoQPKjRwFFPoijcoUyn-9Q&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=d120d20c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cdc.gov.tw/File/Get/UoQPKjRwFFPoijcoUyn-9Q</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:22:55.000Z","msg":"犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />長知識了"},{"pid":"e9fe847c0db182364c16134374f139aa9fc0fb6d","tid":1872801,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5365af5792a6bf838ae9086d151bf28be301f460","tid":1872801,"uid":170229,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"498b832d1bc0c174da3698633619cbf283097729","tid":1872801,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:31:51.000Z","msg":"a,b 3D graphs代表300&micro;m/75&micro;m particles? 點解大粒D穿透會易D"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:43:31.000Z","msg":"借用之前其他連登仔嘅source<br />\n<br />\n台灣cdc:<br />\n<br />\n細小粒徑的微粒本身會有隨 意震動的特性(擴散作用，就像有機蒸氣在靜止的教室前面，慢慢擴散到教 室後面)，再者微粒粒徑越小相同質量下會有更大的表面積，容易產生靜電， 且在帶相同靜電電荷下，靜電力作用會更明顯，這二個擴散及靜電作用，對 於越細小粒徑之微粒都越強烈，因此捕集效率都會增加。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov.tw/File/Get/UoQPKjRwFFPoijcoUyn-9Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov.tw%2FFile%2FGet%2FUoQPKjRwFFPoijcoUyn-9Q&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=d120d20c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cdc.gov.tw/File/Get/UoQPKjRwFFPoijcoUyn-9Q</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"再者微粒粒徑越小相同質量下會有更大的表面積,不過呢個唔係好明,好似有D矛盾"},{"pid":"db633021acb9869325f04c916026f8b32066b674","tid":1872801,"uid":43041,"like":0